<h2>Product report submitted</h2>

<p>A customer has reported a product on Piessang.</p>

<ul>
  <li><strong>Product:</strong> <%= productTitle %></li>
  <li><strong>Product ID:</strong> <%= productId %></li>
  <li><strong>Seller:</strong> <%= vendorName %></li>
  <li><strong>Reason:</strong> <%= reasonLabel %></li>
  <li><strong>Reported by:</strong> <%= reporterName || reporterEmail || reporterUid || "Anonymous" %></li>
  <% if (reporterEmail) { %>
    <li><strong>Reporter email:</strong> <%= reporterEmail %></li>
  <% } %>
  <% if (reportMessage) { %>
    <li><strong>Message:</strong> <%= reportMessage %></li>
  <% } %>
</ul>

<p>Please review the product report in the seller dashboard admin tools.</p>
